<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 83–86" captionStartId="F11" captionText="Figures 83 - 86. Lateral and dorsal habitus images of Lechriopini. 83 a-b Macrocopturus lynceus [SSAC 0001085] 84 a-b Macrolechriops spinicoxis [ARTSYS 0000529]. 85 a-b Microzurus championi [ASUHIC 0031507] 86 a-b Microzygops nigrofasciatus [ARTSYS 0000802]. Scale bars = 2 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.683.12080.figures83–86" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/143836" pageId="29" pageNumber="80">Fig. 84</figureCitation>
